organizations.name: kedah mb more  kedah menteri besar ahmad bashah md hanipah

text:

Kedah Menteri Besar Ahmad Bashah Md Hanipah has been asked to reveal what happened to the RM23.73 million federal allocation for Alor Setar. 
PKR's Alor Setar MP Gooi Hsiao Leung claimed that the RM23.73 million had been distributed to the constituency from May 2013 to September 2016. 
The amount was the Prime Ministerâ€™s special constituency allocation which was distributed to Alor Setar, through the federal development office in Kedah, he added.
